CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 1, 1958, pg. A18, reads: "Honor Grads - Among graduates at the Herron Hill Junior High School commencement program, held last Friday, were (left to right) Mary Ann Mickey, Yvonne Duncan, Regina Wright, Barbara Payne, Linda Sales and Joyce Sharp, who also received the Carnegie Library Award. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of six young women, including Barbara Payne wearing sleeveless dress with diamond patterned crinoline skirt and dark pleated bodice with buttons at waist, after being chosen "Most Outstanding Girl", at Herron Hill Junior High School graduation prom
